  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354560/extras/decaa45a1254bfdfc49c95b24dadac6f.poster.avif?t=1727772025\" width=590 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354560/extras/decaa45a1254bfdfc49c95b24dadac6f.webm?t=1727772025\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a slime looking to get stronger in a weird dungeon, where almost everything is after you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get stronger by finishing dungeons and choose the right upgrades and get the best time possible.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight using your clicks and defend yourself with your shield and good timing ! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Good luck in the dungeon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354560/extras/1fdbca6faf6e5ba91c268c52087f1c4d.poster.avif?t=1727772025\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354560/extras/1fdbca6faf6e5ba91c268c52087f1c4d.webm?t=1727772025\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354560/extras/1fdbca6faf6e5ba91c268c52087f1c4d.mp4?t=1727772025\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lvl Up and choose between randoms upgrades to get stronger !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354560/extras/1db03ef9710498d890a961380f996d72.poster.avif?t=1727772025\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354560/extras/1db03ef9710498d890a961380f996d72.webm?t=1727772025\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354560/extras/1db03ef9710498d890a961380f996d72.mp4?t=1727772025\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354560/extras/decaa45a1254bfdfc49c95b24dadac6f.poster.avif?t=1727772025\" width=590 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354560/extras/decaa45a1254bfdfc49c95b24dadac6f.webm?t=1727772025\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a slime looking to get stronger in a weird dungeon, where almost everything is after you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get stronger by finishing dungeons and choose the right upgrades and get the best time possible.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight using your clicks and defend yourself with your shield and good timing ! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Good luck in the dungeon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354560/extras/1fdbca6faf6e5ba91c268c52087f1c4d.poster.avif?t=1727772025\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354560/extras/1fdbca6faf6e5ba91c268c52087f1c4d.webm?t=1727772025\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354560/extras/1fdbca6faf6e5ba91c268c52087f1c4d.mp4?t=1727772025\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lvl Up and choose between randoms upgrades to get stronger !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354560/extras/1db03ef9710498d890a961380f996d72.poster.avif?t=1727772025\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354560/extras/1db03ef9710498d890a961380f996d72.webm?t=1727772025\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354560/extras/1db03ef9710498d890a961380f996d72.mp4?t=1727772025\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
